reviewText:
Very disappointed, we were looking forward to this video and it was unwatchable!
Sound was unclear and video snowy/black and white/distorted.
Also purchased Comnmunion - enjoyed very much, would recommend this film.

Terrible quality dvd of a vhs transfer. Badly degraded picture very poor quality sound. Home made dvdr!!!!! I didn't know Amazon sold these kind of bootlegs??! Whitley's experience deserve better and so do those like myself who are interested. The link even miss spells his last name!! Beyond Communion - Whitley Srieber
